title: 1996 America's Red Clay Court Championships – Doubles
text: <a href="Todd%20Woodbridge">Todd Woodbridge</a> and <a href="Mark%20Woodforde">Mark Woodforde</a> were the defending champions and won in the final 6–3, 6–3 against <a href="Ivan%20Baron">Ivan Baron</a> and <a href="Brett%20Hansen-Dent">Brett Hansen-Dent</a>.
